value.title: Founders Bay Community
value.description:
About Event

​Kick off 2026 in style as Founders Bay, Space Yacht and The Midway SF team up for an electrifying New Year Holiday Party with music, energy, and great people.

​Hosted by Founders Bay, bringing together the Bay Area tech, creative, and startup community for a night that blends connection and culture.

​The night starts with an early networking hour, then opens into a full-scale show open to everyone.

​Agenda

​9pm - 10pm: Private Founders Bay Mixer
